
[command]
mod

[code]
{delete}
{silent}
{require:serverMod}
{!role $1 +Moderator}
{respond:#channel} The user $1 has been given the {&Moderator} role.

[description]
Allows people with serverMod role or higher to assign the Moderator role to a mentioned user, and announces the user in a specified channel.



